## ğŸ”¨ Development

### Local Development Setup

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/qihoo/google-trends-mcp-server.git
cd google-trends-mcp-server

# Install dependencies
pip install -e .

# Run server
google-trends-mcp-qihoo
```

### Build and Publish

```bash
# Build package
python -m build

# Publish to PyPI
python -m twine upload dist/*
```

